<p><span lang="X-NONE"><span lang="X-NONE">It is important that the Appointing Party's requirements for BIM be considered early so that they can be incorporated into the projectâ€™s BIM processes.</span></span></p>
<p><span lang="X-NONE"><span lang="X-NONE">The completeness of these requirements will depend heavily on the Appointing Party's understanding of the benefits that BIM can bring.&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span lang="X-NONE"><span lang="X-NONE">Our goal is to educate where necessary (in how BIM helps in the operation and maintenance of a building), ask targeted questions and define SMART requirements.&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span lang="X-NONE"><span lang="X-NONE">Here are some of the questions we will ask the Appointing Party:</span></span></p>
